:::
:::

There is very low correlation coefficient of 0.09658636 between product weight and order duration. A correlation coefficient close to zero suggests that there is almost no linear relationship between these variables. In other words, the weight of the product does not have a significant impact on the duration it takes for the order to be delivered. This suggests that the online marketplace's delivery operations are not strongly dependent on the weight of the products being delivered.

